  "id": "RAW_ad39b0f7",
  "title": "估值 1200 亿后 Kimi 再扔王牌，新架构爆改 Transformer 老配件，比 DeepSeek 同款还省钱",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzU1NDA4NjU2MA==&mid=2247658999&idx=1&sn=35ceb204cc3c00397c18bd4fb0a93f2d",
  "date": "2026-03-17 07:51:00",
  "author": "AI前线",
  "siteName": "AI前线",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5454545454545454\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1408\" style=\"width:578px;height:283px;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/lYDricib2fsm52IUKaXTtAquFVt1rj6dkn2iaYbuI4b40NP77gf5YayIj00BRibEgt68aOaYo8r9QcKl3nuvbdV0dU5lkUJESs15luD3Bl0HcIE/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely2=\"283\" data-imgfileid=\"100175335\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=972945c4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FlYDricib2fsm52IUKaXTtAquFVt1rj6dkn2iaYbuI4b40NP77gf5YayIj00BRibEgt68aOaYo8r9QcKl3nuvbdV0dU5lkUJESs15luD3Bl0HcIE%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <div style=\"margin:0;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <p style=\"font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 14px;font-weight: normal;color: #919191;text-align: left;line-height: 1em;margin: 0;margin-top: 13px;padding-left: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">作者 | 允毅 </span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">连马斯克、Andrej Karpathy 都纷纷点赞，DeepSeek 和 Kimi 前后脚都盯上的&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">“残差连接”</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，到底是什么？</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.5212962962962964\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-imgfileid=\"100175340\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7db6be05&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FlYDricib2fsm5wPpv2QpYVsD2PxmAdw0ZCWKLCfTczPtqmA2rccWdbdbXTwenibHzGd8uliaZAsY7vO97JswNpT1AuFu3ibiaFlVsd2RNGRCgicWRQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">最近，Kimi 放出一篇重磅新论文，瞄准一个过去十年几乎没人动过的 Transformer 底层根基：</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">残差连接（Residual Connection）</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。残差连接由何恺明于 2015 年在 ResNet 论文中提出，此后便成为深度学习领域的标配。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">简单来说，可以把大模型的 Transformer 架构，想象成一支几十人排成长队的“传话小组”，那么残差连接就像一条规定：每个工人听完前面所有人的话后，都往里面再补一句，然后原封不动往后传。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">这套规则长这样：</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.20454545454545456\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"440\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-imgfileid=\"100175336\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f3c9b0dd&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FlYDricib2fsm4yeQHubcj2XYLsUXViawBx5nrC2SabgWspAYjpQ8Q1JN81qvgmZJT0QueTuBufTTH4fXtIWlXibVRMJL3UF8Lzv99UD5icdpMp2c%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">但这会带来一个麻烦：队尾的工人收到的话，是前面几十个工人的内容全堆在一起的，越往后话越乱、越长，前面工人说的重点被埋住了，后面工人加的内容也没人听得清，AI 就变笨了。这叫“稀释问题”。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">于是，Kimi 想到把&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">“注意力机制”</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;引进来解决这一问题，它提出一个新的规则：</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">“注意力残差”（Attention Residuals）</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。如同给工人们配备了“智能筛选器”，不用再全盘收下前面堆出来的大杂烩，可以选择重点听前面自己关心的内容。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">结果，AI 变得更聪明了。不仅实现了全场景的稳定提升，在研究生级专业考试、高等数学推理、代码生成、超长文本理解这类真正考验 AI 硬实力的高难度任务上，更是直接实现了 3-7.5 个点的暴涨。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7783783783783784\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"740\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-imgfileid=\"100175338\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=092d6f1c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FlYDricib2fsm4oLWngBoa9leS0QicKOGfRG3zbUBcibYcQ8a90WXlBicrIzlaYzJWCZm1JCYSuJSAY3XwWEEVbdsC7Kp0Mdv3RsN97DG7FDxf3TU%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">而且更省钱了。在 Kimi 自家的大模型架构上验证显示可以节约&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">1.25 倍算力，</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;而训练端到端额外开销&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">不到 4%，</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;推理延迟增加不到 2%，基本没什么额外负担。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.9102941176470588\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"680\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-imgfileid=\"100175339\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b5ba9b2a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FlYDricib2fsm4MBLrJtyic7xbibdSVIwNTQyLkrYLNxibzMfV76rno8j2iatbAdPg6daCGjTrgI30cib1ia6TjX7wibRbfBE7icO4yj31hwIvesslMBLo%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">而且它完全适配大模型的缩放定律，模型规模越大，这套规则的优势越明显。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;font-weight:400;font-size:20px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\"><span data-cacheurl=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" style=\"font-weight: 500;margin: 38px 0 10px 0;height: 59px;line-height: 85px;color: #4285f4;background: none no-repeat 50% 50%;border-bottom: 2px solid #4285f4;background-size: 57px auto;display: inline-block;background-image: url(&quot;https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=67a46bca&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FlYDricib2fsm4eJEnlbfBdbyibYtaH4NEibt4diazcqIQsP0DjU9EqkbsGTNjKic5E5E8Wgib6eYm9BYkYPibqFsAlSgiaJaWTKhl1aicxDqicabCGvLkk%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg&quot;);\"><span leaf=\"\">Kimi 论文里的精彩关注点</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">残差连接之所以能存在这么久，是因为它为 AI 信息的流动开了一条“主干道”，把教 AI 的纠错信号一路传下去，从而让深层网络更容易训练，不会把前面的好东西丢掉。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">但这有三个致命问题改不了，分别是：</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"></p>\n   <ol style=\"list-style-type: decimal;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">不能挑着听：不管是负责“抓重点”的工人，还是负责“整理内容”的工人，都只能听前面堆成一团的话，不能自己选听谁的</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">丢了的内容找不回来：前面工人说的重点，一旦被后面的内容盖住，就再也挖不出来了，AI 聊着聊着就忘了您最开始说的话</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">内容越堆越多：越往后的工人，必须扯着嗓子喊、加更多内容，才能让队尾听到，不然就被前面的内容盖住了，教 AI 的时候很容易教乱套</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ol>\n   <p></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">之前也有不少人想要改善这些顽疾，比如 PreNorm 这种，只是调整内容整理的顺序，完全不改变残差的固定累加规则，完全没改到根子上；或者 MRLA 这类，确实动了规则，但设计太复杂，AI 根本跑不动。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">而 Kimi 的灵感，来自于他们发现，</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">“序列维度上的时间问题和深度维度上的曾问题，本质是同一件事”。</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">当年 AI 读长句子，只能一个词一个词往后传，前面的内容记不住，后来发明了注意力机制，让 AI 能自己选句子里哪个词重要，一下子就解决了。而这和“工人队伍里传话的先后顺序”，本质上是一样的。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">注意力残差链接的具体做法就是：</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">1. 每个工人，都能直接听到前面所有工人的原声，还能打分，分数高就多听，分数低就少听，最后把所有话按分数合起来，再自己加工，传给下一个人</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">2. 打分是不固定的：处理数学题的时候，就多听负责逻辑的工人的话；处理聊天的时候，就多听负责语气的工人的话，特别灵活。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">而公式也变成了这样，其中α就是前面所说，智能筛选器给前面每个工人打的“重要性分数”。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4136460554371002\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"469\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-imgfileid=\"100175337\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=29da8084&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FlYDricib2fsm6pBJicMjbyhaVFnBYxRlhX0uh8xSKXZTiaBbC9cItwDnexibTqibOFoFobacMlibN5UeRPlXnRG1r3uomzOYlcQ3XW3RiaXQlfTiakxU%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">为了让这一套机制真正落地，Kimi 推出了“省力好用版”的注意力残差&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">，即“分块注意力残差”</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">（Block AttnRes）。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">它会把工人分成几个小组，每个小组内部用标准残差连接做累加，类似于“小组总结”，而组与组之间再用 Attention 来做选择性收听。这样一来，大大节省了成本开支。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">为了进一步优化成本，Kimi 团队还做了两项针对性优化：</span></p>\n   <ul style=\"margin: 14px 0 0 0;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"text-align: left;font-size: 16px;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">面向训练过程的&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">“跨阶段缓存”</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：已经传过的旧内容直接存在本地不用反复来回发，每次只传新生成的内容，大幅节省算力、提升训练效率。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"text-align: left;font-size: 16px;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">面向推理过程的&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">“两阶段计算策略”</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：将 AI 生成回复前，先把要用到的历史内容一次性找齐，再一步步算结果，不用每算一个字都重新翻一遍历史，响应更快，用户几乎感知不到任何延迟。</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4102941176470588\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"680\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-imgfileid=\"100175343\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f8713033&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FlYDricib2fsm4FsQcBOY3mSG0X7a2Uce8u6XbBsxW945cE1OFHOjjZHvp2UoxzibdrbxpRL6P2adlnicolztVlXuTZulWsu3KuZFebIlLTcmj0c%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">最后，Kimi 实际测试了 5 种不同大小的 AI，从 194M 到 528M，分对比了传统残差连接、注意力残差连接和分块注意力残差的实际效果。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">结果发现：</span></p>\n   <ul style=\"margin: 14px 0 0 0;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"text-align: left;font-size: 16px;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">不管 AI 是大是小，注意力残差连接都比传统残差连接犯错更少、更聪明</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"text-align: left;font-size: 16px;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">分块注意力残差连接，花同样的钱，能达到传统残差连接 1.25 倍算力才能达到的效果</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"text-align: left;font-size: 16px;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">AI 规模越大，分块版和完整无损版的注意力残差连接效果越接近，超大 AI 里，两者几乎一模一样</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.2968591691995948\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"987\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-imgfileid=\"100175345\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=184b08e2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FlYDricib2fsm4KBGibAJQXdoPb8H6CIBCSYQ0Ux9pO4wahaBhib6yXMVtahCrTjAhv9iabia2CGPahuA5Ysib8HndBP62M7YJXickRtXQUiaufVpEN6I%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">Kimi 还做了一系列消融实验，证明注意力残差连接中的每个设计，都必不可少：</span></p>\n   <ul style=\"margin: 14px 0 0 0;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"text-align: left;font-size: 16px;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">必须用“随内容变的打分”，如果用固定的分数，效果就很差，甚至不如传统残差连接</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"text-align: left;font-size: 16px;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">必须用 softmax 打分，不然 AI 就不会果断选重点，效果变差</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"text-align: left;font-size: 16px;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">必须先把内容整理通顺再打分，不然信息容易盖住其他人，效果变差</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"text-align: left;font-size: 16px;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">分成 8 个左右的小组，效果最好</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">Kimi 的新设计给了 OpenAI 大神 Andrej Karpathy 不少启发，他忍不住深思，“注意力机制”是不是可以运用到更多的地方去？</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100175341\" data-ratio=\"0.48333333333333334\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%; pointer-events: initial;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1073c0d6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FlYDricib2fsm6Zsvtzo6DfL0aRaNqlsKz0JibfBO7zXtvRTP2NzUSS9nUX1ic9XicI7vuvPNt0GcjWI3XpyR7QeVmM4Bsp5ibvuHiaJISHsjibIM4z8%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">有网友直接指出，或许 Transformer 中不少“长期沿用的配置”，都可以动一动了。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4131994261119082\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"697\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-imgfileid=\"100175344\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6a567e37&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FlYDricib2fsm4icYY3Cr2GXoQzdFTVpGATSrKdEYBRF135MHURqRUQDsSH81BIDlqF009I308Pl2dpf9eTGcVSlJNibQ2ib5H7NiaIB98piaA8bYtQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">还有网友激动地将 Kimi 奉为“新的 DeepSeek”。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7276657060518732\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"694\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-imgfileid=\"100175342\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ba987f0f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FlYDricib2fsm4DBhFEuReSkicxrwYPtNQXZsCUlwqPvbCcca9yrJtwNrcYYxk6tMOXpxM41mf5QMDr8jBznAhT9X9nMDaYDehD00OdTbLCDEzw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <div data-role=\"outer\" label=\"edit by 135editor\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n    <div data-role=\"paragraph\">\n     <div style=\"margin:0;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"margin:0;font-size:20px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\">\n       <p><span data-cacheurl=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" style=\"margin: 38px 0 10px 0;height: 59px;line-height: 85px;color: #4285f4;background: none no-repeat 50% 50%;border-bottom: 2px solid #4285f4;background-size: 57px auto;display: inline-block;background-image: url(&quot;https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=dd59e942&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FlYDricib2fsm6zUqC1uJSItEMoTLAvhJA1cgl23DxotMEoagMnpiavHqN9j02oqsXt59nASCribdpib62bm2q0c3uI2WUq3r3poHPTVWiaRFKJkT4%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg&quot;);\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">DeepSeek 与 Kimi 的</span></span></strong></span></p>\n       <p><strong style=\"background-color: initial;color: rgb(66, 133, 244);caret-color: red;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">解法有什么不同？</span></span></strong></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">虽然都是对残差连接进行创新，但 DeepSeek 推出的 mHC 却和 Kimi 的 AttnRes 走出了两条路。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果把残差连接理解成 AI 内部的一套“传话机制”，那两家的分歧，首先来自于它们对“问题到底出在哪”的判断不同。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">DeepSeek 的思路是，信息主干道太挤，信息才会乱，那就拓宽多条并行专线，用学习好的规则在专线之间混合、传递。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">Kimi 的思路则是，信息主干道不能挑重点才会乱，那就给筛选权。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">这也带来了两者在能力边界上的关键差别，DeepSeek 的做法只能听到 “混合后的二手内容”，听不到原版原话，而 Kimi 的做法能直接听到 “所有前面的原版原话”，想找谁的就找谁的。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">两者都能提升基础效果，但擅长的领域完全不同，差距主要在复杂任务上。</span></p>\n   <ul style=\"margin: 14px 0 0 0;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"text-align: left;font-size: 16px;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">mHC：主打 “训练稳定性”，基础能力有提升，复杂任务乏力</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">它的核心价值是能把模型做的更深，训练的时候不会乱套，解决了深层模型训练崩溃的问题，在基础的语言理解、闲聊场景有稳定提升。但在需要多步推理、长上下文记忆、精准逻辑回溯的任务上，比如数学、代码、专业考试、长上下文问答，提升非常有限 。原因正在于它不擅长让模型“精准找回某个早期关键步骤”。</span></p>\n   <ul style=\"margin: 14px 0 0 0;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"text-align: left;font-size: 16px;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">AttnRes：兼顾稳定性 + 复杂推理，长上下文 、逻辑题提升碾压</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">它不仅解决了深层模型的训练稳定性问题，更擅长需要精准回溯、多步推理的高难度任务。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">两者在落地适配性上天差地别。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">DeepSeek 的 mHC 更像伤筋动骨的大改造，得把现有 AI 的单流架构完全改成多流并行架构，每层都要加新的流处理模块，还要重调全套训练参数，没法直接替换传统残差连接，老模型基本没法直接升级，跟拆房重盖没两样，适配成本极高。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">而 Kimi 的 AttnRes 是即插即用的替换件，只需要把模型里原来的残差连接模块换成 Block AttnRes，其他模型结构、训练参数全都不用动，老模型直接升级就能拿到效果提升，就像给房子换个好门锁不用拆墙，适配成本极低。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">从已有对比看，Kimi 似乎拿到了更好的“性价比”。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">有网友将 Kimi 的 AttnRes 将与 DeepSeek 的 mHC 进行了性能对比，发现在 Kimi 的消融实验中，Kimi 完整无损版本的 Full AttnRes 性能始终优于 mHC，而 Block AttnRes 的性能与之相当，但 Kimi 的方案需要读写的数据量，只有 DeepSeek mHC 的 1/6。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">这意味着，在大模型真正走向大规模工程部署的语境下，Kimi 的路线可能具备更强的现实吸引力。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">过去十年，Transformer 的大部分创新都集中在注意力、FFN、MoE、位置编码和训练数据上。残差连接则像空气一样存在，重要，但过于基础，以至于几乎没人认真去动它。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">而现在，DeepSeek 和 Kimi 先后出手，或许正释放一个信号：当数据红利逐渐到顶，过去的大模型比拼的是“谁能堆更多算力，那么下一代大模型，或许要开始学会“管信息”来拉开差距。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: bold;\">参考链接：</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><a href=\"https://github.com/MoonshotAI/Attention-Residuals/blob/master/Attention_Residuals.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/MoonshotAI/Attention-Residuals/blob/master/Attention_Residuals.pdf</a></span></span></p>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Kimi 发布新论文提出「注意力残差连接」（Attention Residuals），通过引入注意力机制解决 Transformer 残差连接的稀释问题，在保持效果的同时实现 1.25 倍算力效率提升，获得 Andrej Karpathy 等业界大佬点赞。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Kimi 发布新论文提出「注意力残差连接」（Attention Residuals），通过引入注意力机制解决 Transformer 残差连接的稀释问题，在保持效果的同时实现 1.25 倍算力效率提升，获得 Andrej Karpathy 等业界大佬点赞。",
  "summary": "文章深入解析 Kimi 最新论文中对 Transformer 架构底层组件「残差连接」的创新改进。针对传统残差连接导致的「稀释问题」，Kimi 提出「注意力残差连接」机制，为每层引入「智能筛选器」，让模型能够选择性地关注前面层的重要内容。进一步提出「分块注意力残差」以降低计算成本，配合「跨阶段缓存」和「两阶段计算策略」等优化手段。实验表明，该方法在研究生级考试、数学推理、代码生成等硬任务上实现 3-7.5 个点的提升，且达到传统残差 1.25 倍算力才能达到的效果。文章还对比了 Kimi 与 DeepSeek mHC 方案的不同思路。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "传统残差连接存在「稀释问题」，信息逐层累加导致后面层难以聚焦关键内容。",
      "explanation": "类比传话小组，后面工人收到的是前面所有人内容的堆叠，重点被淹没，导致 AI 变笨。"
    },
    {
      "point": "注意力残差连接引入「智能筛选器」，让每层可以选择性关注前面层的重要内容。",
      "explanation": "通过可学习的注意力权重给前面层打分，重要的多听，不重要的少听，解决稀释问题。"
    },
    {
      "point": "分块注意力残差在保持效果的同时大幅降低计算成本，实现 1.25 倍算力效率。",
      "explanation": "将层分成小组，组内用标准残差，组间用注意力，既保留选择性又节省开支。"
    },
    {
      "point": "Kimi 与 DeepSeek 对残差连接的改进代表了两种不同思路：选择性收听 vs 多路并行。",
      "explanation": "Kimi 让模型挑重点听原版原话，DeepSeek 拓宽多条专线传混合信息，两者适用场景不同。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "可以把大模型的 Transformer 架构想象成一支几十人排成长队的传话小组。",
    "如同给工人们配备了智能筛选器，不用再全盘收下前面堆出来的大杂烩。",
    "分块注意力残差连接，花同样的钱，能达到传统残差连接 1.25 倍算力才能达到的效果。",
    "或许 Transformer 中不少长期沿用的配置，都可以动一动了。"
  ],
